    "2e), 0.889 (pitch f 0, Fig. 2f), 0.812 (first formant f 1, Fig.",
    "2f) and 0.883 (second formant f 2, Fig. 2f).",
    "Accurate reconstruction of the speech parameters, especially the pitch, voice weight and first two formants, is essential for accurate speech decoding and naturalistic reconstruction that mimics a participant's voice.",
